MedicationRequestSubjectIdentifierSearchParameter

Parameter subject.identifier:token

Searches for MedicationRequest by the patient identifier eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/MedicationRequest?subject:Patient.identifier={identifier}

ResourceMedicationRequest
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesMedicationRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
